      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You're here. Great. I have another gig for you. #b#p403##k, sitting in front of the subway station, needs help. A friend of hers gave her a puppy as a present a few days ago, and she's looking to make a cute, comfortable doghouse for him."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I think I just need you to defeat #b25 #o11#s#k and bring #b15 #t4000011#s#k. It'll be a breeze for someone like you, so please don't make that poor puppy wait out in the cold any longer than he has to! Come back to me as soon as you have them—I'll be waiting."
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I like you. You know how to take care of business. Alright, here's your reward. #b#p403##k is giving you a bunch of hand-made #b#t2020002#s#k."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright, if you need work sometime down the road, feel free to come back and see me."
        }
      },
